extension_description.message: Copy links from the current webpage to clipboard in various formats.

settings_description_tooltip.message: Append description to link text. (Only when description data exists on the page) [Space]

settings_line_break_tooltip.message: Append a line break at the end of link text.

settings_group_help_link.message: Click the button to toggle the display of links, and drag to reorder them.

settings_group_help_description.message: [Space] key to toggle the display of description.

message_select_link_format.message: * Please select a link format to display.
